Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\shad0\bord2\frz1.5\fs34\t(\fs32)\move(364.797,35,364.797,54,24,7323)\c&&HC9D4D7&}Warning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:03.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Viewers Sitting in Front of the Television,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:05.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the guys that appear in this anime are delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, please do not imitate what you see in this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\b1\i0\bord0\blur0.3\fad(450,0)\c&HDADADA&\fs33\pos(362.532,49)}Do not imitate{\i1\fs40}!{\i0\fs33} Or this will happen{\i1\fs40}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}僕が泣いているのは とても悔しいからです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}Boku ga naite iru no wa totemo kuyashii kara desu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)}The reason I am crying is\Nbecause I am very frustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}人の尊さやさしさ 踏みにじられそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Hito no toutosa yasashisa fuminijiraresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}I feel as though the nobility and\Nkindness of man is being trampled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}力を示す者達は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Chikara o shimesu mono tachi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}しなやかさを失って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Shinayakasa o ushinatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:34.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Those who show their strength lose their grace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}ウソまみれドロまみれ じれったい風景でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uso-mamire doro-mamire jirettai fuukei desho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Covered in dirt and lies, isn't it a vexing sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}より強くしたたかに タフな生き方をしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Yori tsuyoku shitataka ni tafu na ikikata o shimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's live more strongly, fiercely, and tougher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}まっすぐ歩きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Massugu arukimasho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's walk straight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}風は向かい風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kaze wa mukai kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The wind is against us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ どけ どけ 後ろめたい奴はどけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke doke doke ushirometai yatsu wa doke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, move, move, those with\Na guilty conscience, move aside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}有象無象の町に 灯りをともせ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uzoumuzou no machi ni akari o tomose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Light up the town of riffraff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ そこ どけ 真実のお通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke soko doke shinjitsu no otouri da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, make way, truth is coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}正義の時代がくるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Seigi no jidai ga kuru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The era of justice will come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}希望の歌もあるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kibou no uta mo aru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}There are songs of hope too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}僕の命この世に 捧げてしまっていいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}Boku no inochi kono yo ni sasagete-shimatte ii sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)}I would happily sacrifice my life for this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:32.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My name is Takeshi Hokuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:36.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm the heir to the Hokuto Foundation,\None of the major Japanese financial groups,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:38.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and my martial arts ability is also top-notch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:43.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Money, power, and strength...\NI'm a man with everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:46.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You can say that I was surely born to be a ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:51.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,By the way, I transferred to\N Cromartie High School by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:53.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hokuto! There's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:54.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:57.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Haven't you heard of the Boss Championship?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:01:58.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:02.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's a tournament that decides\Nwho the No. 1 boss in Japan is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:06.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? A tournament that decides\Nthe No. 1 boss in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:10.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The Japan Boss Championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:14.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It is a prestigious tournament that\Ndetermines the highest-ranked boss in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:17.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Leaders from delinquent schools\Ngather once a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:21.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It has been held every year,\Nexcept for the year of the Oil Shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:24.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Right then, all of Cro-High was\Nalso talking of nothing but that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:28.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How careless of me, not knowing\Nabout such a tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:34.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Be that as it may, why didn't\NI hear about it until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:36.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I hate to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:39.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but isn't it because you don't\Nhang out with your friends much?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:42.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Just the other day, everyone said,\N"let's go to karaoke,"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:46.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but you said that you wanted\Nto watch TV and went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:48.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is a good opportunity,\N so let me say that you're losing friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:52.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, you idiot?!\NI have many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:55.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then who are your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:58.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,First of all, you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:02:59.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So your list {\i1}starts{\i0} with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:04.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm your junior, rather than a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:08.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it,\N I really don't have any specific friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:09.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If only I had gone to karaoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:12.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, shut up! Don't treat me\Nlike I'm one of the masses!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You don't have friends because you're like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Are you still saying that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:20.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In the first place,\N making friends is something silly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:25.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the powerless, foolish masses do\Nto seek emotional support!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:28.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,As the man who will become\Nthe future ruling monarch of Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:30.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I need not bother with such worthless things!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:33.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you understand, it's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:35.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, are you going to participate\Nin the tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:37.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:39.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But it's kinda tough to join them and tell them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:43.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,that you want to participate\Nwhen you're not even invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:45.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You aren't invited either?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:47.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I was just listening in from the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:51.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they're hesitant to invite me now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:54.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,since I turned down\N the karaoke invitation that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:59.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't mind going then,\Nbut I just don't like singing that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:00.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:02.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's fine if it's just listening to others' singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:05.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In fact, I like listening to good singers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:08.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But in that kind of situation,\Nit's almost always the case
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:11.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,that there are guys who stick a mike\Nin your face, saying "Sing!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:15.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you turn it down, it could ruin the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:18.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm the type who's very\Nconcerned about others, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:19.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:21.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I don't want you to misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:24.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean I'm a bad singer,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:26.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,though some guys say something\Nlike that right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:28.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I just don't like singing, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:30.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If anything, I think I'm actually a good singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:32.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So are you going to participate\Nin the tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:34.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:36.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm not talking about a karaoke tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:37.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:41.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I certainly apologize for\Ndiverging from the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:43.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But it's a plain fact that we're at a disadvantage
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,that we're not invited\N even if we want to participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:49.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If we just go and talk to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:51.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,it'll look as if we're asking them\Nso that we can participate,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:54.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and that's the one thing my pride won't allow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:57.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What should we do? Do you have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:59.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:03.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We'll make an appeal to them again\Nabout how incredible you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:07.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then even those idiots will notice\Nthat they need you and beg you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:10.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,saying "please participate."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:15.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But it's hard to make those fools see\Nmy brilliance and my high caliber.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:18.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll assist you in that part. Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:24.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Got it. I'm counting on you... er... you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.72,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur0.4\fnLauren C. Brown\shad0\c&H131312&\b1\pos(625.367,84)}{\alphaff}aaa{\alpha00}You\N {\b0}(Hokuto's lackey)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:29.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Around that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:33.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,all the classroom chatter was about\Nthe Japan Boss Championship,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:36.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and a heavy, dangerous atmosphere\Nwas filling the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:40.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I am definitely opposed to\Nsuch a violent tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:44.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I'd like to ask, just in case,\Nwhat's the prize for the winner?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're not planning to participate, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:49.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But you know, this tournament\Nis incredibly tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To participate representing the Tokyo area,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:55.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,you have to be someone who is suitably strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:57.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You small fry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:00.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're Hokuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:07.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We're busy right now,\N so could you go somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:14.43,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(358,390)}Hokuto's lackey
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:10.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:13.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It seems that you don't know how incredible Mr. Hokuto is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:14.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll explain it to you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:18.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's so incredible about him?\NWhy don't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:22.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,First of all, he's a person of high caliber.\NTo Mr. Hokuto, you guys are tiny little things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:27.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see, high caliber? And how high is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:33.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, you've been talking about Japan's\NNo. 1 boss or something like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:35.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To Mr. Hokuto, that's already a little thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:37.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If No. 1 in Japan is a little thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,does that mean that he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's right! To put it bluntly,\Nhe's at the world level!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:45.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So unlike you guys, he doesn't bother\Nwith small stuff in little Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In short, does that mean that\N he's aiming to become the world's boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:49.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't really get it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:52.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect this. Hokuto's really incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:55.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I feel that the conversation\N is off the point somehow again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:58.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's something I'd like to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:03.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In order to become the world's boss,\Nwhat do I have to do first?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:06.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't know much about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:07.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but one thing I can say without a doubt is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:11.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That we don't need you here at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:15.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Do your best and become the world's boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:18.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I can also see you off without worries!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:21.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Courage is springing up in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:23.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, then! Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:29.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What kind of boss is the world boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:35.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,After school, behind the school building\Nat Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:40.68,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(504.146,390)}Takashi Kamiyama (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:40.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}Then, Hayashida, you look\N like your father? I wanna see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:44.94,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(186.93,394)}Takeshi Hokuto (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:44.94,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(504.146,394)}Shinjiro Hayashida (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:44.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but my dad doesn't have a mohawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:44.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:48.28,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(504.146,390)}Takashi Kamiyama (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:48.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}Come to think of it, Maeda, you definitely\Nlook like your mother, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:53.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(203.924,394)}Shinjiro Hayashida (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:53.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(542.665,394)}Akira Maeda (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:51.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, as you all know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:53.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's incredible, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:58.04,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(430.506,388)}Main character Takashi Kamiyama (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:58.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it... Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:05.00,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(430.506,388)}Main character Takashi Kamiyama (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:05.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}You, which do you look like,\Nyour father or mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:07.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Just "you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I look like my grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What, like your grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:14.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,By the way, did you have a dream\Nwhen you were a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How about you, Hokuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mine was conquering the world, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:23.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Freddie, what was your dream\Nwhen you were a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:28.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even if you talk to Freddie,\Nhe won't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:31.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's even uncertain whether he had a childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:33.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And, let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:37.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:38.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:41.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You've been calling me just "you"\Ninstead of my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:43.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please call me by name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:46.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that you don't know my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:51.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:53.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No way! You don't know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:55.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've been in this school for half a year already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:58.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hokuto, we've known\N each other for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,so there's no way you don't\Nknow my name, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:02.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:06.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Seriously?! And don't say it\Nwithout hesitation like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:09.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The reason that we didn't know your name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:12.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Because we didn't think it mattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:15.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You use that calm tone, but say some\Npretty mean things, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Damn it! I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:20.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then you'd be happy if I introduce\Nmyself again, right?! My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:22.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,By the way, I'm changing the subject, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:25.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hayashida! To say the least,\Nthat's rude, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:28.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hayashida, that's indeed too rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:30.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let's just quietly hear his name now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:33.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It certainly was a little childish of me. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:36.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Thanks, though it sounds strange to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:39.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'll introduce myself. My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Freddie spilled juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:44.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll clean it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:48.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right? Listen carefully. My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:50.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We don't have any juice left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm so thirsty that I could die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:53.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Fine! I'll go and buy it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:58.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right, then! I'll tell you my name!\NMy name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:01.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's trouble! A fight started\Nin the class next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:03.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I got it. You'd be happy if I go there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.29,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs42\fad(0,100)\fnArial\blur0.4\pos(358,410)}Thirty Minutes Later
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:08.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I beat them all up good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:09.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Is he serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:11.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Were you that strong a fighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:16.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Are there any other troubles?!\NI'll solve them all, so tell me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:17.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:20.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right, then! All the problems\Nhave been taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:23.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now I can tell you my name without any worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:26.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay? Listen carefully! My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:30.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's trouble! A meteorite has fallen\Non the school building!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's beyond my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:45.04,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\fnEdo SZ\shad0\bord0\c&HE3E2E2&\move(115.557,89,115.557,117,0,12953)}Japan Boss\N Championship
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:35.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Will the day come when\N Hokuto's lackey's name is made clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:38.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What will happen to the Boss Championship?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:40.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In the next episode of\N "Sakigake!! Cromartie High School,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:43.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,there will be stuff with all the answers\Nand also stuff without them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:45.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We hope you'll be looking forward to seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:45.01,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\alpha130\fs24\fnNeon\bord0\c&H4E1728&\blur0.5\pos(346.671,139)}Next\N\N\N\NEpisode
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.01,0:11:50.02,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs26\blur0.5\fnArial Black\bord3\c&H000000&\3c&HFBFAFC&\pos(203.924,50)}Sakigake!!\NCromartie High School
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:50.02,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs26\blur0.6\fnArial Black\bord3.2\c&H000000&\3c&H3F3F3F&\pos(203.924,50)}Sakigake!!\NCromartie High School
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:50.02,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\shad0\fs36\bord2.2\blur0.5\pos(376.127,390)}What's wrong with "Hokuto's lackey"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:36.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sakigake!! Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:39.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,True feelings clash against each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:41.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Forge ahead as it comes to you.\NThe first one to say it wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:44.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It will eventually\N work out somehow. Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right? My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:49.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We're out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Intro Warning,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\blur0.3\pos(213.928,323.39)}When you are watching television
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Intro Warning,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\blur0.3\pos(587.096,341.559)}please have the room\Nbrightly lit and be\Ncareful not to get too\Nclose to the screen.
